{"word":"ψήχω","slug":"ψήχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ψήχω</b></el> <el>(ψήχω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ψάω'><el>ψάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to rub down, curry</i> a horse, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: — <i>to stroke, pat</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>mulcere</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to rub down, wear away</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}